    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Ours is out in tofino &#8211; where we drop our crab trap when the tide is out with hot dogs as bait (they work!) and if we&#39;re lucky feast on fresh crab, steamed in sea water, with garlicky butter and corn bread. With friends! No better way to eat crab.</p>
    </div>

